CONTEST ENDED AND WINNER ANNOUNCED International Winter Blues Give❄️away

We’re joining together to offer up a cure for the winter blues with these Wordsworth Classics. Each host will pick a winner and that winner can choose TWO titles from our stack (watch the reel to see all the titles)

To enter:
❄️Follow all hosts:
	@thenerdybookwormsblog
	@kayckay_bookreviews
	@bookstasamm
	@rva_reader
	@rozierreadsandwine
	@purrfectpages

❄️Like and save this reel
❄️Share to your stories
❄️Tell us which two titles you’d pick

💫We will never ask you to click on any links via DM. Beware of spam and impersonation accounts. Neither IG nor FB is affiliated with this book party. 
Ends 1/23. Open internationally as long as Book Depository ships to you. Winner will need to provide name and postal address. 

⚠️ Folks who follow to unfollow will be blocked from future giveaways.

